&gt;&gt;Ian Ni-Lewis: On the Worldscope Webcams.

00:02:22.700 --> 00:02:29.230
Andrea Baccega of Fast Booking and Ryan Oldenberg
from Hipmunk who is joining us live in the

00:02:29.230 --> 00:02:30.230
studio.

00:02:30.230 --> 00:02:31.230
&gt;&gt;Reto Meier: Very exciting.

00:02:31.230 --> 00:02:33.920
