00:02:48.800 --> 00:02:49.800
Whatever.

00:02:49.800 --> 00:02:50.800
&gt;&gt;Reto Meier: Exactly.

00:02:50.800 --> 00:02:51.800
It's just too hard.

00:02:51.800 --> 00:02:53.380
&gt;&gt;Ian Ni-Lewis: Let's go ahead now and look
at Worldscope Webcams.

00:02:53.380 --> 00:02:54.670
&gt;&gt;Reto Meier: Alright.

00:02:54.670 --> 00:02:59.130
So, let's start off by putting up on screen
the ratings that we gave this app.

