And he already told me some of those things,
he told me one of those is really to use the

00:10:28.011 --> 00:10:33.280
first application screen as a view pager so
you'll be able to swipe left and right but

00:10:33.280 --> 00:10:36.890
in that case I think I will leave the map
tab completely out and put it somewhere else.

